                    <td class="forumAlternate" >Bards aren't &quot;ruined&quot; in EQ2 and they are not &quot;just like every other class.&quot;  The four main archetypes play very differently and scouts are really quite different from fighters, mages, and priests.

Within the scout archetypes, bards are quite different from predators and rogues.  Predators are all about damage -- they dish out massive doses of it, especially when they're in a group where the mob has it's back turned.  Rogues do plenty of damage, as well, and also have a few tricks that ...</td>
